Version 0.2.1 - 2015-04-01
==========================
	* CHANGES:
	- Add missed error check in is_empty_fp().
	- Change indent style.
	
	* OPTIMIZATIONS:
	- Tiny code optimization.
	- Remove unnecessary headers include.


Version 0.2.0 - 2015-02-22
==========================
	* CHANGES:
	- The prompt option '--ask, -i' removed.
	- The two long options '--overwrite' and '--output-to-beginning' removed.
	- Docs updated to be compatible with the code.
	- Update copyright year.
	
	* OPTIMIZATIONS:
	- Add and use safe_fclose() to close opened files.
	- fxor now use less code and less source-code files.
	- Tiny optimizations in fxor docs.


Version 0.1.2 - 2014-11-01
==========================
	* NEW:
	- Add README.md
	- Add scripts/opssl_rand.sh; the script takes IN_FILE_NAME size and run openssl command
		to make a random file (OUT_FILE_NAME), So OUT_FILE_NAME_SIZE = IN_FILE_NAME_SIZE
	
	* OPTIMIZATIONS:
	- Remove unused code "Read one byte test from streams in_f and key_f" in <src/fxor.c>
	- Update fxor description.
	- Tiny optimizations in fxor docs.


Version 0.1.1 - 2014-10-14
==========================
	* FIXED BUGS:
	- fxor_stream_xor() in <src/fxor_stream_xor.c> return wrong number when the key is empty.
	
	* OPTIMIZATIONS:
	- Reduce hearders dependencies in <src/is_empty_stream.c>
	- Tiny optimizations in fxor docs.
	- Other optimizations and tiny bugs fixing.


